Title: Lit
Presenters: Obligatory Undead Panel: Is Undead Dead
Book Description: Mary Lynne Gibbs, Michael Cieslak, Sean M. Davis, Ken MacGreggor
All Day Event: 'Shoot ‘em in the head- stake ‘em through the heart- the good old silver bullet...it doesn’t matter- the undead keep coming back.  Have zombies- vampires- and werewolves finally run their course or do these creatures still have legs?  Is there a division between genre fans who have grown tired of these creatures just as they’re taking off in the general public?'
